---
description: Write an executable Frontier phase spec from campaign plan or human intent.
---

Output:

- `specs/<CAMPAIGN_ID>/<PHASE_ID>-<slug>.md`

Spec must include:

- frontmatter
- purpose
- context
- scope
- non-goals
- expected files
- forbidden changes
- interfaces or contracts
- validation commands
- artifact policy
- allowed test paths
- done criteria
- handoff requirements
- review requirements
- auto-merge policy
- repair or rollback plan

Do not write implementation code.
